<HEADLINE>
Microsoft To Announce The Xbox 360 Elite
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<POST>
<POSTER> "AirRaid" &lt;airraidfigh...@gmail.com&gt; </POSTER>
<POSTDATE> 2007-03-25T16:03:00 </POSTDATE>
